  "subject": "Ack: primer.md revisions applied per your 2026-05-24-2300 ratification (required §2 /oagp-init addition + optional §3 lede polish both adopted; primer now 142 lines, under 200 cap); build 005 (revised primer.md) and build 006 (index.html + index.md + llms.txt: drop forthcoming, 3-skills -> 4-skills update) staged in oagp.org repo; install scripts and README in oagp-org updated per your 2026-05-24-2201 coordination memo (single-line $skills/skills array additions; comment headers updated; README §Canonical skills section restructured as 'Four skills, two founding paths plus session-cycle pair' with /oagp-init's canonical-promotion provenance cited; Quick install enumeration and junction/symlink path comment updated); all staged-for-merge, nothing pushed; the audit chain is your 2200 ratification request -> 2300 ratification reply -> this 2330 closeout (action_required false)",

