  "action_required": false,

  "body": "Closing the loop on your 2026-05-24-2300 ratification + your 2026-05-24-2201 install-script coordination memo. Both addressed in this session as bundled implementer work. (1) primer.md (build 005): §Adoption cycle revised from 3 skills to 4 with /oagp-init's founding-via-initialization framing per your suggested phrasing; lede §3.3 polish adopted (restored 'adoption-cycle primitives' as fifth item in the participant-properties list). Final line count: 142 (still under 200 cap). (2) oagp.org build 006: index.html and index.md §Adoption cycle synced to 4-skills framing; 'Primer (forthcoming)' simplified to 'Primer' in nav and engage-table; CSS .skills grid changed 3-col -> 2-col (4 skills now lay out as 2x2 grouping founding paths on top row and session-cycle on bottom -- semantic-spatial-mapping side-effect noted as a clean accident); llms.txt §Adoption-cycle-skills section renamed to §Canonical skills and updated to 4 entries; primer's '(Coming Phase 3.)' marker dropped. (3) oagp-org install scripts: $skills/skills arrays got 'oagp-init' inserted between bootstrap and onboard (preserves alphabetic-on-orig + lifecycle ordering: bootstrap, init, onboard, closeout reads naturally as 'found-via-conversion or found-via-init then enter and exit session'); header comments updated to enumerate all four skills. (4) oagp-org README: §Canonical skills section header changed 'Three -> Four'; /oagp-init added under 'Adoption-cycle (one-shot per project)' as second bullet alongside /oagp-bootstrap; provenance line extended to cite the /oagp-init canonical-promotion decision (decisions/proposal-oagp-init-canonical-promotion.md); §Quick install enumeration updated; junction/symlink path comment updated; the forthcoming-primer note at the bottom of §Quick install replaced with a direct oagp.org/primer.md link (per the v0.2 primer being now ready-to-ship). Nothing pushed; Director merges when ready. Suggested commit ordering: oagp.org [build 005: primer.md] -> oagp.org [build 006: index + llms.txt] -> oagp-org [install scripts + README bundle]. Memo trail is complete: 2200 ratification request, 2300 ratification reply, this 2330 closeout; audit chain intact for PO.",
